title: Karmanu Icon Pack v2.5 APK (Android)
description:
Features:
1. 2750+ icons (and growing)
2. 80+ HD 3000x2675 px cloud-based wallpaper for direct access to newest wallpaper
3. XXXHDPI Icon 192x192 px
4. Full manually vector graphic processing icons
5. Icon masking for better unthemed icons
6. See & Search all icons
7. Smart Icon Request
8. Support Muzei
9. Image picker, attach as an image to email, hangouts, Etc or even use it to create Zooper widget
10. Dinamic calendar support (including Google and Today Calendar)
11. Help section, contains FAQs with search function
12. Report bugs
13. Show/Hide launcher icon from app drawer
14. etc

Support 22 major Launchers:
L (New)
Lucid (New)
GO
Next
Apex
Action Pro
Nova
ADW
Holo
Holo HD
TSF Shell
LG Home (read issue for this launcher below)
Themer
CM Theme Engine
Launchy Widget
Trebuchet
Unicon
And much more that have icon pack support
Note:
GO, Next even Mini Launcher doesn't support Icon Masking, so go to preferences > Icons > TICK OFF "show icon base".
Downloaded wallpaper. Find them on /Pictures/Karmanu/wallpaper/HERE
LG Home may working unstable for some device. DO NOT PURCHASE IF YOU'RE NOT SURE!
What's in this version : 
Added 100+new icons
Added and fixed a lot of activities
Previously added 45 new wallpapers to cloud
Required Android O/S : 4.0+
